HEADWORD: Gloam
<hw>Gloam</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The twilight; gloaming.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Keats.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gloaming</ent>⟦br⟧
